volunteer_experiences.description:
As part of the first board of the Young Statisticians (YS) Division of the Netherlands Society for Statistics and Operations Research (VVSOR), I set up this division in order to provide a platform for Young Statisticians, research master students, and young professionals interested in research. The main objectives of the YS are to:

- broaden the professional network of students and young professionals;
- promote the field of statistics and its broad applications;
- get acquainted with the variety of research positions within private sector and academia.

I have also been part of the Web Committee (February 2012-March 2013) and The Statistical Science Café Committee (May 2011-December 2014).
